<p>
<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">svastiśrī</hi> kulottuṅkacoḻateva
<lb n="2" break="no"/>ṟku yāṇṭu Ēḻāvatu kāṅkayattil viyā
<lb n="3" break="no"/>pāri moṭan ceṭṭiyāna Īcāna tevanne
<lb n="4" break="no"/>n muttūr Āḷuṭaiyār kulottuṅ
<lb n="5" break="no"/>kacoḻī<hi rend="grantha">śvara</hi>muṭaiyāṟku cantiyātīpam
<lb n="6"/>Onṟukkum Accu Onṟu kuṭukkaik koṇṭu
<lb n="7"/>Ikkoyililk kāṇiuṭaiya civappirā
<lb n="8" break="no"/>maṇaṟk kācuvan paṭṭan Uṭaiyāṉāna kulatīpa pa
<lb n="9" break="no"/>ṭṭannen Enmakkaḷ makkaḷ Ivviḷakkoṉ
<lb n="10" break="no"/>ṟum cantirātittavarai celvatākavum 
</p>

